a.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice D'Amato\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\"}, {\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9521089381033256, \"rank\": 0.03537534015317634, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"big names\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 236}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 324}, {\"ngram\": \"the chances\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gymnastics title\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, she had qualified a lowly seventh amongst the eight finalists and had never won an individual medal at a major global meeting, and this was not even an apparatus the asymmetric bars specialist exceled at.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eight finalists\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual medal\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"a major global meeting\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"even an apparatus\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"the asymmetric bars specialist\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after seeing errors from top qualifier Zhou Yaqin, who grabbed the apparatus with both hands to save herself slipping off, and with Lee crashing to the mat mid routine, the 21-year-old D'Amato unexpectedly gained a chance to sneak into medal contention with a clean routine.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.9999288041151561, \"rank\": 4.861133151746841e-05, \"text\": \"Zhou\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_dynasty\"}, {\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yaqin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\"}, {\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9992763123747657, \"rank\": 0.000724209071912068, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"errors\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"the apparatus\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"both hands\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"mid routine\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the 21-year-old D'Amato\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"medal contention\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"a clean routine\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She moved securely and confidently through her routine, sticking her dismount and clapping with a smile to celebrate her strong performance that earned her 14.366, well short of the top qualifying mark of 14.866.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"her dismount\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"her strong performance\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"the top qualifying mark\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Biles and Rebeca Andrade yet to show off their skills on the 10-cm-wide apparatus, D'Amato must have thought she had secured the bronze when she saw her name on top of the standings.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1195, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their skills\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10-cm-wide apparatus\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"D'Amato\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the standings\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On any other day, her display might not have been enough for the win but a fall from Biles and a less than stellar performance by Andrade paved the way for D'Amato's historic victory.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999963129085, \"rank\": 3.6836990115979404e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any other day\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"her display\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"a fall\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"a less than stellar performance\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"D'Amato's historic victory\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Beating Simone and Sunisa was only possible because both of them fell off the beam,\\\" D'Amato said, adding that she had benefited from this \\\"stroke of luck.\\\"\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunisa\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"the beam\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"D'Amato\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"this \\\"stroke\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But this is how a beam final works.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how a beam final works\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one who can best withstand the pressure, use it to her advantage and perform the best exercises will win.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The one\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"her advantage\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"the best exercises\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, this person was me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this person\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"D'Amato, who also won silver with Italy in the team event, has a twin sister, Asia, who is also a gymnast on the Italian team but had to sit out the Paris Games with a knee injury requiring surgery.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_footbal